表的代码预览业务-公告提醒表

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_noticeremind')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_noticeremind
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_noticeremind */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_noticeremind (
RemindID int identity,
AdminID int not null,
NoticeID int not null,
constraint PK_BUSI_NOTICEREMIND primary key (RemindID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_noticeremind') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'业务-公告提醒表',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_noticeremind')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'RemindID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind', 'column', 'RemindID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'提醒ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind', 'column', 'RemindID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_noticeremind')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'AdminID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind', 'column', 'AdminID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'操作人ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind', 'column', 'AdminID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_noticeremind')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'NoticeID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind', 'column', 'NoticeID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'公告ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticeremind', 'column', 'NoticeID'
go
